> Sports Another blocked punt helps Saints top Falcons, 31-21 Atlanta Falcons running back Devonta Freeman (24) runs toward the end zone for a touchdown against New Orleans Saints strong safety Kenny Vaccaro (32) during the second half of an NFL football game, Thursday, Oct. 15, 2015, in New Orleans. (AP Photo/Gerald Herbert)
